txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Huge filth from insects and spiders from the lands surrounding Aughaire. Deliver the items to Raith at Aughaire in the south-western reaches of Angmar.
'We will use this well. Thank you.'
'There are uses for the filth that comes from insects and spiders. If you are willing to collect it for us, it would be welcome.'
Council of the North Task: Huge Filth
The Hillmen at Aughaire have requested a collection of huge filth to be delivered to Raith.
Deliver the huge filth to Raith at Aughaire in Angmar
You have accepted a task to collect and deliver huge filth from insects and spiders surrounding Aughaire to Raith, a Hillman within the settlement.
Wanted: Huge filth from insects and spiders from the lands surrounding Aughaire.
